{
  "stem": "20800.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We work together.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had even a-- a contact with the prison-- men prisoners, which were a few kilometers from our prison working on the factories, too, that way of working.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was a factory who produce part for the aircraft.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was working as a welder.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- parts to the, actually, plane-- to the airplane.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because I never weld-- and I didn't now-- they have to teach me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I make sure they teach me long enough.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, it's when master come and look at me, I make a hole.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oh, you're not ready yet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I was waiting-- they were waiting long enough-- me, to be ready to weld it properly.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We weld not only [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] iron, but we weld aluminium.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "All sort of things we weld.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were-- we were working on the gas-- bicarbonate gas, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--how you call it, the cylinders.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But two cylinders we have to put this-- actually, weld that to the two cylinders, and it-- to put the fire to-- to weld.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, that gives me opportunity to get in touch with the man's concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The cylinders was brought by the prisoners of the next men's concentration camp on the-- how you call-- trolley, you would call.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The cylinders was lying on a trolley.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And about four or five of them were bringing this trolley to the place-- special place in the corner.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we-- if we needed, we have to tag the cylinders, put down there light-- there empty, and tag the full one to put back to be able to work.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was one prisoner which is-- was, like, a head of this group, used to look at me when I was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
